      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "QUEST FOR STEPS (1) below best last time at this track (17.75) in a Free For All, finishing a 10 length sixth. Makes strong appeal on best. BLUE LACE (2) failed to come into contention last start after settling well back at this track, but prior to that won by 1.75 lengths at this track (17.33) beating Aston Paycheck in a Grade 5/6 on July 3. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Better than last start and can bounce back. SON OF SPIKE (3) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 3.5 lengths win at this track in a handy 17.30. Has a low draw and likes the trip. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to feature again. JAFFA'S MONELLI (8) cannot be dismissed although new to this distance.",
